Nijiro Murakami

1035
02:04:31,590 --> 02:04:35,420
"You're always here with me"

1036
02:04:38,060 --> 02:04:41,800
"Cause in my bones I feel"

1037
02:04:41,800 --> 02:04:43,430
Kanichiro

1038
02:04:44,640 --> 02:04:48,470
"An invisible power levitating me"

1039
02:04:48,470 --> 02:04:50,670
Kento Hayashi

1040
02:04:51,140 --> 02:04:53,540
"Someday again"

1041
02:04:53,540 --> 02:04:55,250
Rico Narumi

1042
02:04:55,250 --> 02:04:57,520
"We'll find each other"

1043
02:04:57,520 --> 02:04:59,580
Mugi Kadowaki

1044
02:04:59,580 --> 02:05:02,610
"So say goodbye till then"

1045
02:05:07,460 --> 02:05:13,730
"Though I can't touch you anymore"

1046
02:05:13,970 --> 02:05:18,670
"I still feel you in the air"

1047
02:05:20,310 --> 02:05:26,840
"This song is the proof of life we led"

1048
02:05:27,450 --> 02:05:33,320
"With these words on my lips"

1049
02:05:33,620 --> 02:05:41,220
"I'll sing for you instead"

1050
02:05:42,630 --> 02:05:48,120
"Yes, from the bottom of my heart"

1051
02:05:53,040 --> 02:05:57,070
"Ever wondered where"

1052
02:05:59,640 --> 02:06:03,450
